sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as Gateway
    participant RB as Ring Buffer
    participant ME as Matching Engine
    participant L as Ledger
    participant K as Kafka
    participant AI as AI Pipeline
    participant R as Redis

    C->>G: Submit Order (gRPC)
    activate G
    G->>G: Validate & Auth
    G->>RB: Publish Event
    activate RB
    RB-->>G: Acknowledge
    G-->>C: Order Accepted
    deactivate G

    RB->>ME: Process Batch
    activate ME
    ME->>ME: Match Orders
    ME->>L: Update Balances
    activate L
    L-->>ME: Settlement Complete
    deactivate L
    ME->>K: Publish Trade Event
    activate K
    K-->>ME: Persisted
    deactivate K
    ME-->>RB: Complete
    deactivate ME
    deactivate RB

    par Async AI Processing
        K->>AI: Consume Event
        activate AI
        AI->>AI: Agent 1: Anomaly Detection
        AI->>AI: Agent 2: RAG Lookup
        AI->>AI: Agent 3: Decision
        AI->>R: Update Circuit Breaker (if needed)
        AI-->>K: Processing Complete
        deactivate AI
    end

    Note over C,R: Happy Path: <1ms matching, <200ms AI
